●	Solution-
1.	Start system.
2.	Wait for feeding time.
3.	If feeding time = time in clock  → check container food level.
4.	If food available in container → rotate motor to drop portion.
5.	Wait 10 minutes.
6.	Check if bowl weight decreased means the pet ate the food.
7.	If yes → return to idle and do nothing . If no → send message
8.	If container empty → send message immediately.
